data.enText: the use of living cells and bacteria in industrial and scientific processes

tr: the branch of engineering science in which biological science is used to study the relation between workers and their environments
the branch of molecular biology that studies the use of microorganisms to perform specific industrial processes
example: biotechnology produced genetically altered bacteria that solved the problem

value.def: Biotechnology is the use of living parts such as cells or bacteria in industry and technology.

example.tran: 将蛋白质转化为药品的生物技术专家
